931
01:17:43,665 --> 01:17:46,209
Oh, Jesus.

932
01:17:51,256 --> 01:17:53,675
You are not going anywhere, young lady.

933
01:17:53,758 --> 01:17:56,970
You stay right there.

934
01:18:02,725 --> 01:18:04,686
Where are they?

935
01:18:05,937 --> 01:18:07,856
Where the hell are the drugs?

936
01:18:07,939 --> 01:18:09,983
Where are they?

937
01:18:10,108 --> 01:18:12,026
Fuck you.

938
01:18:12,152 --> 01:18:14,112
Fuck you.

939
01:18:14,195 --> 01:18:18,324
I wasn't doing anything.
