Um... I was waiting
for the right time.

1454
02:15:44,086 --> 02:15:47,339
Oh. You didn't think you could trust
my wife with that information?

1455
02:15:47,465 --> 02:15:49,508
I didn't want to risk it.

1456
02:15:49,633 --> 02:15:52,178
