1459
02:15:56,640 --> 02:16:00,186
raise my kids, sleep in my bed...

1460
02:16:00,311 --> 02:16:02,521
with my wife.

1461
02:16:02,646 --> 02:16:04,900
Sounds like a nice plan.

1462
02:16:05,025 --> 02:16:06,985
Oh, is it insane?

1463
02:16:07,068 --> 02:16:09,696
Just think about it, okay?
If I was gonna rip you off,

1464
02:16:09,821 --> 02:16:12,032
