after Ruiz was killed?

1465
02:16:12,157 --> 02:16:15,327
Why would I sit next to you
in court and listen to a dismissal?

1466
02:16:15,410 --> 02:16:19,706
Let me ask you something.
You think there's a difference
between a reason and an excuse?

1467
02:16:19,831 --> 02:16:22,375
'Cause I don't.

1468
02:16:22,501 --> 02:16:25,796
- Good-bye, Arnie.
- Carl--

1469
02:16:25,921 --> 02:16:27,881
