1478
02:16:57,370 --> 02:16:59,789
- You're--
- How you doing?

1479
02:16:59,872 --> 02:17:02,291
- What are you doing in my house?
- Oh, just looking around.

1480
02:17:02,375 --> 02:17:05,795
You got nice shit. Drug money
buys a lot of nice shit, Carl.

1481
02:17:05,878 --> 02:17:08,214
