You remember that!

1491
02:17:40,872 --> 02:17:43,124
- What's his problem?
- The carpet, sweetheart.

1492
02:17:43,249 --> 02:17:45,168
- No, no, no, I got it.
- I got it.

1493
02:17:48,255 --> 02:17:50,299
