02:18:56,658 --> 02:19:00,870
I just want to grab the phone
and start dialing numbers.

1502
02:19:00,995 --> 02:19:04,707
I want to pull my hair...

1503
02:19:04,791 --> 02:19:09,045
and run through
the streets screaming.

1504
02:19:13,508 --> 02:19:18,555
But thanks to the people
I've met in these rooms,

1505
02:19:18,680 --> 02:19:22,892
like Margaret and Jim...

1506
